  [38;2;177;185;249mBuffer::head [mand [38;2;177;185;249mBuffer::scrollbackUsed [mare plain [38;2;177;185;249mint [m— NOT atomic. Reader thread writes them in [38;2;177;185;249mscrollUp()[m, message thread reads them in [38;2;177;185;249mscrollbackRow() [mand
   [38;2;177;185;249mgetScrollbackUsed() [m[1mwithout[22m [1msynchronization[22m. The [38;2;177;185;249mresizeLock [mdoes NOT gate reader-thread scroll operations.[K[50C
