  When CC generates heavy output, the reader thread calls [38;2;177;185;249mscrollUp(N) [min a loop. If the message thread wakes mid-loop for [38;2;177;185;249monVBlank[m:[K[28C
  - [38;2;177;185;249mhead [mis partially incremented → [38;2;177;185;249mscrollbackRow() [mcomputes wrong physical index[K[78C
  - [38;2;177;185;249mscrollbackUsed [mis stale → [38;2;177;185;249mvisibleStart [mcomputation is off[K[98C
  - Snapshot reads rows from wrong ring positions → visual duplication[89C
