  This is the SSOT violation you suspected. The shadow isn't a cached copy — it's [1mthe[22m [1mraw[22m [1munsynchronized[22m [1mread[22m [1mof[22m [1ma[22m [1mvalue[22m [1mbeing[22m [1mmutated[22m [1mon[22m [1manother[22m [1mthread[22m.      
